title: Emtek E2200 Classic Style Electronic Keypad Leverset w/ Storeroom/Gate Function
item_description:
Emtek E2200 Classic Style Electronic Keypad Leverset w/ Storeroom/Gate Function

  • Fits standard door thickness of 1-3/4 in. Please specify if thicker.
  • Standard door prep 2-1/8 in. bore
  • Standard latch is for 2-3/8 in. backset. 2-3/4 in. available.
  • Factory programmed with 2 unique, 4-digit secure user codes for use right out of the box.
  • Can be programmed with up to 20 user codes of your choice.Add, edit, and delete user codes from your device.
  • Illuminated keypad for easy and quick operation after dark.
  • Low battery indicator lets you know when to change the battery.
  • Keypad has a protective coating to prevent wear patterns.
  • Storeroom/Gate Function: Outside lever always locked. Entry by code or key only. Inside lever always free
